{"type": "USJ", "version": "3.1", "content": [{"type": "book", "marker": "id", "content": ["53-2TH-web.sfm English Arabic Names Version (EANV)"], "code": "2TH"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "ide", "content": ["UTF-8\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "h", "content": ["2 Thessalonians \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc1", "content": ["Paul\u2019s Second Letter to the Thessalonians \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc2", "content": ["2 Thessalonians \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc3", "content": ["2Th \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "mt1", "content": ["Paul\u2019s Second Letter to the Thessalonians \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "1", "sid": "2TH 1"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "2TH 1:1"}, "Paul, Silvanus, and Timothy, to the assembly of the Thessalonians in Allah our Father, and the Lord Al Masih Isa:\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "2TH 1:2"}, "Grace to you and peace from Allah our Father and the Lord Al Masih Isa.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "2TH 1:3"}, "We are bound to always give thanks to Allah for you, brothers,", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": [" \n", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:3 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["The word for \u201cbrothers\u201d here and where context allows may also be correctly translated \u201cbrothers and sisters\u201d or\n\u201csiblings.\u201d"]}], "caller": "+"}, " even as it is appropriate, because your faith grows exceedingly, and the love of each and every one of you\ntowards one another abounds, \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "2TH 1:4"}, "so that we ourselves boast about you in the assemblies of Allah for your perseverance and faith in all your persecutions\nand in the afflictions which you endure. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "2TH 1:5"}, "This is an obvious sign of the righteous judgement of Allah, to the end that you may be counted worthy of Allah\u2019s Kingdom,\nfor which you also suffer. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "2TH 1:6"}, "Since it is a righteous thing with Allah to repay affliction to those who afflict you,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "2TH 1:7"}, "and to give relief to you who are afflicted with us, when the Lord Isa is revealed from heaven with his mighty angels in\nflaming fire, \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "2TH 1:8"}, "punishing those who don\u2019t know Allah, and to those who don\u2019t obey the Good News of our Lord Isa,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "2TH 1:9"}, "who will pay the penalty: eternal destruction from the face of the Lord and from the glory of his might,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "2TH 1:10"}, "when he comes in that day to be glorified in his saints and to be admired amongst all those who have believed, because\nour testimony to you was believed. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "2TH 1:11"}, "To this end we also pray always for you, that our Allah may count you worthy of your calling, and fulfil every desire of\ngoodness and work of faith with power, \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "2TH 1:12"}, "that the name of our Lord Isa", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:12 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["TR adds \u201cMasih\u201d"]}], "caller": "+"}, " may be glorified in you, and you in him, according to\nthe grace of our Allah and the Lord Al Masih Isa. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "2", "sid": "2TH 2"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "2TH 2:1"}, "Now, brothers, concerning the coming of our Lord Al Masih Isa and our gathering together to him, we ask you\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "2TH 2:2"}, "not to be quickly shaken in your mind, and not be troubled, either by spirit, or by word, or by letter as if from us,\nsaying that the day of Masih has already come. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "2TH 2:3"}, "Let no one deceive you in any way. For it will not be, unless the\nrebellion", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["2:3 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["or, "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "fqa", "content": ["falling away"]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": [", or, "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "fqa", "content": ["defection"]}], "caller": "+"}, " comes first, and the man of sin is revealed, the\nson of destruction, \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "2TH 2:4"}, "he who opposes and exalts himself against all that is called Allah or that is worshipped, so that he sits as Allah in the\ntemple of Allah, setting himself up as Allah. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "2TH 2:5"}, "Don\u2019t you remember that, when I was still with you, I told you these things?\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "2TH 2:6"}, "Now you know what is restraining him, to the end that he may be revealed in his own season.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "2TH 2:7"}, "For the mystery of lawlessness already works. Only there is one who restrains now, until he is taken out of the way.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "2TH 2:8"}, "Then the lawless one will be revealed, whom the Lord will kill with the breath of his mouth, and destroy by the\nmanifestation of his coming; \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "2TH 2:9"}, "even he whose coming is according to the working of Iblis with all power and signs and lying wonders,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "2TH 2:10"}, "and with all deception of wickedness for those who are being lost, because they didn\u2019t receive the love of the truth,\nthat they might be saved. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "2TH 2:11"}, "Because of this, Allah sends them a working of error, that they should believe a lie;\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "2TH 2:12"}, "that they all might be judged who didn\u2019t believe the truth, but had pleasure in unrighteousness.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "2TH 2:13"}, "But we are bound to always give thanks to Allah for you, brothers loved by the Lord, because Allah chose you from the\nbeginning for salvation through sanctification of the Spirit and belief in the truth,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "2TH 2:14"}, "to which he called you through our Good News, for the obtaining of the glory of our Lord Al Masih Isa.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "2TH 2:15"}, "So then, brothers, stand firm and hold the traditions which you were taught by us, whether by word or by letter.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "2TH 2:16"}, "Now our Lord Al Masih Isa himself, and Allah our Father, who loved us and gave us eternal comfort and good hope through\ngrace, \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "2TH 2:17"}, "comfort your hearts and establish you in every good work and word.\n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "3", "sid": "2TH 3"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "2TH 3:1"}, "Finally, brothers, pray for us, that the word of the Lord may spread rapidly and be glorified, even as also with you,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "2TH 3:2"}, "and that we may be delivered from unreasonable and evil men; for not all have faith.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "2TH 3:3"}, "But the Lord is faithful, who will establish you and guard you from the evil one.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "2TH 3:4"}, "We have confidence in the Lord concerning you, that you both do and will do the things we command.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "2TH 3:5"}, "May the Lord direct your hearts into Allah\u2019s love, and into the perseverance of Masih.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "2TH 3:6"}, "Now we command you, brothers, in the name of our Lord Al Masih Isa, that you withdraw yourselves from every brother who\nwalks in rebellion, and not after the tradition which they received from us.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "2TH 3:7"}, "For you know how you ought to imitate us. For we didn\u2019t behave ourselves rebelliously amongst you,\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "2TH 3:8"}, "neither did we eat bread from anyone\u2019s hand without paying for it, but in labour and travail worked night and day, that we\nmight not burden any of you, \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "2TH 3:9"}, "not because we don\u2019t have the right, but to make ourselves an example to you, that you should imitate us.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "2TH 3:10"}, "For even when we were with you, we commanded you this: \u201cIf anyone is not willing to work, don\u2019t let him eat.\u201d\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "2TH 3:11"}, "For we hear of some who walk amongst you in rebellion, who don\u2019t work at all, but are busybodies.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "2TH 3:12"}, "Now those who are that way, we command and exhort in the Lord Al Masih Isa, that they work with quietness and eat their\nown bread. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "2TH 3:13"}, "But you, brothers, don\u2019t be weary in doing what is right. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "2TH 3:14"}, "If any man doesn\u2019t obey our word in this letter, note that man, that you have no company with him, to the end that he may\nbe ashamed. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "2TH 3:15"}, "Don\u2019t count him as an enemy, but admonish him as a brother.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "2TH 3:16"}, "Now may the Lord of peace himself give you peace at all times in all ways. The Lord be with you all.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "2TH 3:17"}, "The greeting of me, Paul, with my own hand, which is the sign in every letter: this is how I write.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "2TH 3:18"}, "The grace of our Lord Al Masih Isa be with you all. Amen. "]}]}